<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="2Dec1938"><font color="red">2 December 1938</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Richard de la Mere to Paul L&eacute;on) Thank you for your letter of November 26th with which you sent me a further revised typescript for the last pages of Mr Joyce&apos;s book. I will let the printers have it &hellip; [and] ask them to return us the previous copy, which shall come back to you shortly &hellip;  </div>
